<header class="single-header">
<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
</header>
<div class="single-content">
<p>Please find our privacy policy here: <a href="https://www.degruyter.com/cms/pages/privacy-policy">https://www.degruyter.com/cms/pages/privacy-policy</a>.</p>
<p>We use certain tools on our website, which enable the evaluation of user behaviour on the website and the placement of target-group-specific advertising. We use cookies or similar technologies for this purpose.</p>
<p>To withdraw your consent you can reach our consent center with a click on the icon “C” in the left lower corner of the screen on our main website <a href="https://www.degruyter.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">www.degruyter.com</a>.</p>
</div>
</article>
</section>
